_UJ_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UJ admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UJ admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444270\">About the University of Johannesburg (UJ) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444271\"><strong>How to Apply for UJ Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444272\">Documents Required for UJ Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444273\">UJ Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444274\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"#_Toc80444275\">Applying for Financial Assistance in UJ<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80444276\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UJ admission 2024?<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-university-of-johannesburg-uj-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_University_of_Johannesburg_UJ_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444270\"><\/a>About the University of Johannesburg (UJ) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the University of Johannesburg(UJ) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80444271\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for UJ Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.uj.ac.za\/studyatUJ\/sec\/Pages\/International-Applicants.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-uj-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_UJ_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444272\"><\/a>Documents Required for UJ Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<li>Sworn English Translation of documents (Documents issued in any language other than English)<\/li>\n<li><strong>Should you require on campus accommodation, please submit a completed residence\u00a0application form at the same time you apply to study at UJ<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"uj-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"UJ_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444273\"><\/a>UJ Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee of R200 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R200<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444274\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30\u00a0September 2024\u00a0at 12:00 noon<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-uj\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_UJ\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444275\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in UJ<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application portal<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.uj.ac.za\/studyatUJ\/Student-Finance\/Documents\/NSFAS_and_Bursary_online_consent_and_upload_of_document_process.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-uj-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_UJ_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80444276\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for UJ admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"UJ Online Application for Admission in 2024, University of Johannesburg Application 2024 fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status, Closing&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1114,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1113"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1113"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1113\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"